name: 567 BET
about: When you download or play our games, we do not collect any personally identifiable information about you, such as your name, address, phone number or email address. If you email us, we will retain your email content in order to respond to your questions or in the event we need to provide you with a better experience. If you subscribe to our email list, we do maintain the information you supply in order to communicate with you about game updates and other previously-disclosed marketing purposes of our own - never for others.
